{
  "title": "Deliciously Dense Norwegian Fish Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and comforting Norwegian fish stew featuring hotsauce and nimono-simmer, perfect for a sick day, this low-fat-friendly dish is sure to warm your belly and your soul.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
